These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Pet: hedgehog, horse, rat, chinchilla
Food: peach, pepper, pomegranate, nectarine
1. Pet:hedgehog is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1
2. Food:nectarine is on the far left##1
3. Food:pomegranate is between Food:pepper and Pet:horse##2
4. Pet:chinchilla is on the far left##1
5. Pet:rat is between Pet:horse and Pet:hedgehog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | chinchilla         | horse   | rat | hedgehog       |
| Food      | nectarine | peach | pomegranate   | pepper |

