.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Game: billiard, monopoly, scrabble, backgammon
Pet: dog, goldfish, horse, guinea-pig
1. Pet:guinea-pig is between Game:scrabble and Pet:goldfish##2
2. Game:backgammon is on the far right##1
3. Pet:horse is on the right of Pet:dog##1
4. Game:billiard is on the left of Pet:dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | monopoly | billiard | scrabble | backgammon |
| Pet   | goldfish    | guinea-pig   | dog | horse       |

